{"tid":2451932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"全智賢屈居季軍 大韓空姐嚴選真人最靚女星","createTime":"2021-03-18T12:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:48:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6cd267daf95ff595d97a65afa428b86b1375b22","tid":2451932,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4OpWlR2rJ9L9MTER62Qf6IRQW28=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXXJZW756FBWXNCV6SQKCKQOU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4OpWlR2rJ9L9MTER62Qf6IRQW28%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXXJZW756FBWXNCV6SQKCKQOU4.jpg&h=00555a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國不少女星搭飛機時都愛素顏示人，幕前幕後的樣貌會有很大變化，人前人後亦有機會兩個樣。近日有一名在大韓航空當了8年空姐的YouTuber就在頻道上選出「真人也十分漂亮的女演員」，當中韓國女神全智賢僅排季軍位置，冠軍則落在有「韓國第一大美人」之稱的43歲金喜善身上，亞軍則為韓劇《春夜》、《耀眼》的38歲女星韓智敏。<br />\n<br />\n全智賢素顏示人<br />\n該名空姐YouTuber表示依舊記得全智賢展現「藝人氣場就是這樣的」的演員，透露當日全智賢雖然素顏示人，形容她長髮飄飄走進了頭等艙。同時表示全智賢在飛機上更換舒適的衣服後，就戴上耳機欣賞電影，空姐YouTuber續說：「她吃拌飯吃得很滋味的樣子令我印象深刻。全智賢不是有點漂亮，而是有一種很美的感覺。」事實上，全智賢的樣貌一向獲不少圈中人稱讚，當中在神劇《來自星星的你》中飾演千頌伊（全智賢飾）經理人角色的金康鉉受訪時也直認全智賢是他見過的所有女藝人中，真人最漂亮的一個。<br />\n<br />\n韓智敏坐經濟艙<br />\n提到亞軍的韓智敏時，空姐YouTuber形容：「小小的臉上裝着眼睛、鼻子和嘴，她雖然個子不高，但有着不現實及完美比例的小臉。當時她穿着登山服這麼樸素的衣服進入機艙時，身後似乎有光環照耀着。她有特有的活力，清爽得像人類的維他命一樣。」最令人意外是韓智敏竟然是乘坐經濟艙。<br />\n<br />\n金喜善散發女性美<br />\n至於獲封為冠軍是擁有防腐美貌的金喜善，金喜善屬20世紀90年代最紅的美女，亦具有票房保證，當年不少整容外科醫生們都稱讚金喜善的臉龐是完美的左右對稱。空姐YouTuber表示：「金喜善散發出美麗的女性美。在機內用餐後要求收拾盤子時，她會很禮貌及鄭重地拜託我們。她不僅開朗，而且性格也很好，看上去更漂亮，電視上只能看到金喜善十分之一的美貌。」<br />\n<br />\n女神密密拍廣告<br />\n另外，現年39歲的全智賢雖然已屬兩子之母，但仍無損她廣告女王的地位，近日她又成為樽裝水的代言人，同時其代言的服飾品牌又公開她的新廣告硬照，硬照中可見全智賢瞓在浴缸內大擺甫士，相當可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0BUanNGxr_XnHLwCVaHuF1vt_KM=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJKNRZVISZEOBLASQFRN7S2SSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0BUanNGxr_XnHLwCVaHuF1vt_KM%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJKNRZVISZEOBLASQFRN7S2SSM.jpg&h=11c9a2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RJoFrZKKhn-3b3sPl5O264Tv67M=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QCAMXWOOOBCW5D3IZ6EXZWX2AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRJoFrZKKhn-3b3sPl5O264Tv67M%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQCAMXWOOOBCW5D3IZ6EXZWX2AY.jpg&h=1681ef02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JMDwrOJr_OibTYkGBbxICSOTAUY=/802x1001/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y3DY6GXLA5CVXO2C4RTWV2PDWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJMDwrOJr_OibTYkGBbxICSOTAUY%3D%2F802x1001%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY3DY6GXLA5CVXO2C4RTWV2PDWI.jpg&h=4c3ae6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oXfx0GItuBTOgdAi1McOBqukZs0=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZPKUWPHJ7ZCLVPMIXY6XMB5TXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoXfx0GItuBTOgdAi1McOBqukZs0%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZPKUWPHJ7ZCLVPMIXY6XMB5TXU.jpg&h=894aaf93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JAZbWTMOP-wpptItBTkvYHEfAHk=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/65WGRIX2TVFW5L3KGTWJGL3XDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJAZbWTMOP-wpptItBTkvYHEfAHk%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F65WGRIX2TVFW5L3KGTWJGL3XDU.jpg&h=6711fd9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/HKAPOSQZNNDT5AFCYFFLXZHSMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FHKAPOSQZNNDT5AFCYFFLXZHSMY%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2bTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=4e70ef92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FHKAPOSQZNNDT5AFCYFFLXZHSMY%2F&h=01584602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/HKAPOSQZNNDT5AFCYFFLXZHSMY/</a>"},{"pid":"a68f73d01bb17aa5f814be0f6124e7b87caa2de9","tid":2451932,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"勁靚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3771abb387d222c13fcb61529fd58c90377e7a1","tid":2451932,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"金喜善 個樣好老套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f48b420d29194ee08158c729a94fe8a541d7246","tid":2451932,"uid":146556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3771abb387d222c13fcb61529fd58c90377e7a1","tid":2451932,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"金喜善 個樣好老套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"女人評女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\